criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age greater than 60 years;

          -  is not engaged in physical exercise programs for at least one year;

          -  do not present severe cardiovascular disease, kidney disease, liver disease or
             limiting cognitive or neuromuscular disease and;

          -  does not present visual or auditory inability.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  failing to perform any of the evaluations suggested during the intervention protocol
             and;

          -  absence in five or more Capoeira training sessions.
